description: Daughter of history sheeter Kanhaiya Yadav died during police raid on his house in Manrajpur village of Chandauli district. The girl died after she was reportedly beaten up by the SO leading the raid. Kanhaiya Yadav’s second daughter too suffered injuries as she tried to cut her veins. Villagers held a violent protest against the police and damaged an ambulance. The government has suspended the SO who led the raiding party. Senior officials say Kanhaiya Yadav was not found at his residence and the cops tried to take away his brother. The gangster’s daughter protested this move, and she she suffered grievous injures as she was beaten up by the SO.
